{"tid":2076562,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府撥110萬元賑濟廣西水災","createTime":"2020-06-23T15:16:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T15:41:23.000Z","uid":320680,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f09600176d1e35fb20a94384409a2e5f7785adb8","tid":2076562,"uid":320680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T15:16:33.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】政府宣布批出兩筆，共110萬元的撥款，賑濟廣西水災災民。<br />\n<br />\n撥款將會平均給愛德基金會和樂施會兩間賑災機構，將會為約1萬2千名災民購買糧食。<br />\n<br />\n政府強調，兩間機構會在不同地方進行救援工作，資源不會重疊。<br />\n<br />\n賑災基金諮詢委員會要求兩間機構完成賑災後，向委員會呈交評估報告及經審核的帳目，確保撥款用於指定用途。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%92%A5110%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83%E8%B3%91%E6%BF%9F%E5%BB%A3%E8%A5%BF%E6%B0%B4%E7%81%BD-104537769.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E6%2592%25A5110%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2585%2583%25E8%25B3%2591%25E6%25BF%259F%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E7%2581%25BD-104537769.html&d=91nyg34XrGq4aGOua7i4JSrXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=b1be9d5c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%92%A5110%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83%E8%B3%91%E6%BF%9F%E5%BB%A3%E8%A5%BF%E6%B0%B4%E7%81%BD-104537769.html</a><br />\n<br />\n快啲多謝政府啦，又攞我哋啲錢送中<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ebf6427edd6ae1f91869494c7e31e2fd650af94","tid":2076562,"uid":78513,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T15:19:23.000Z","msg":"110萬都唔夠香港起條欄杆 <br />\n林鄭係咪想搞港獨？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cde2734ee49bed7b953b5a07ebb6f243504189d8","tid":2076562,"uid":343361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T15:19:25.000Z","msg":"你哋唔捐呀嘛<br />\n政府幫你哋捐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" cla